Acknowledgments:

  This project uses the triple inverted pendulum benchmark parameters
  originally published by G.A. Medrano-Cerda at the University of Salford, UK (1997).
  See: "Robust stabilization of a triple inverted pendulum-cart,"
  International Journal of Control, 68(4), 849-865.

